{"tid":2103461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★fatfat！歐洲消費者組織向 Apple 施壓  要求就電池問題每人賠償 60 歐元","createTime":"2020-07-11T08:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T18:52:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6f99f252a1ad87c9c1d15075495b930366b571bf","tid":2103461,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"近日，一個由五個消費者組織組成的團體 Euroconsumers 就要求 Apple 向所有用戶賠償，並威脅指未有回覆將採取法律行動追討損失。<br />\n<br />\nApple 在過去多年一直因令舊 iPhone 運作速度變慢而延長電池壽命一事遭到多方的指控，而據外媒在近日最新的報道，由比利時、西班牙、葡萄牙、意大利以及巴西五個國家的消費者組織所組成的團體 Euroconsumers 在日前就事件再向 Apple 追討賠償，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>要求 Apple 向受影響的 iPhone 用戶每人賠償 60 歐元</strong></span>，指出 iPhone 電池壽命無故地大幅縮短無疑是 Apple 故意所導致。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據報道中指出，是次 Euroconsumers 決定向 Apple 提出賠償申請是參考了 Apple 去年曾就事件被法國政府罰款 2500 萬歐元以達成和解的一案，故此同樣參考相關做法追討賠償。Euroconsumers 表示目前已先後於 6 月 11 日以及 7 月 2 日向 Apple 發信<span class=\"xx-large\">要求對方於 15 天內做出回應，並明確表示一旦未獲回覆將採取法律行動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/11/europe-presses-apple-for-more-iphone-batterygate-compensation/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F11%2Feurope-presses-apple-for-more-iphone-batterygate-compensation%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=58a36b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/11/europe-presses-apple-for-more-iphone-batterygate-compensation/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"af87454a7537028a71bbc404deb6640f91d778dd","tid":2103461,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" c